            userId: s.userId,
            userName: s.user.name || "Unknown",
            amount: s.amount.toNumber()
        }))
    }));

    // 3. Calculate Member Standings (Who owes whom in this group)
    // We'll calculate: (Sum of Splits Owed) - (Sum of Expenses Paid)
    // Actually simpler: For each member, their balance = (Amount they PAID for the group) - (Amount they are OWED as a split)
